s if you wish to do so, and if you prefer not to receive any promotional and marketing communications, please withdraw from this option at any time.<br><br>We may give your name and address to a third party in order to deliver to you your purchase order (for example, delivery agent or supplier).<br><br>We may be able to store details about your current order on our website but we cannot retrieve it directly for security reasons. By logging into your account on the site, you can see the information and details of your purchases that you have requested or that will submit soon. You are also able to manage your address details. You should also pledge to deal with complete confidentiality when entering your personal data, so do not make it available to an unauthorized third party. We are not responsible for any misuse of passwords unless this misuse is caused by our fault.<br><br>Other uses of your personal information<br>We may use your personal information in surveys and marketing research, at your discretion, for statistical purposes while ensuring its complete confidentiality, and you have the right to withdraw at any time. We do not send any answers to any third party. Your email address is not disclosed unless you wish to participate in the competitions. We keep your survey answers completely separate from your private email.<br><br>We may send information about us, or about the site or our other sites, or about our products, our sales, our sales offers or our newsletters, and other things related to the companies of our group or our partners. If you do not wish to obtain this additional information (or any part of it), please click on the “unsubscribe” link in any e-mail sent to you, and we will stop sending this information to you within seven working days (every day except for days) Saturday, Sundays, and national and religious holidays) from receiving your notification. We will contact you to inquire about the information when it is not clear.<br><br>We may use some data, while fully preserving the privacy and confidentiality on the site, for other purposes, including verifying the whereabouts of users and following up on their visit to the site or links in the e-mail while they subscribe to receive it, and to provide that anonymous data, which does not allow your personal identity to be identified. The actual fact, to a third party such as publishers, for example. However, this data will not identify you (because it is not personally identifiable).<br><br>Competitions<br>In relation to any competition, we use the data to notify the winners and to advertise our offers. You can find more details about the conditions for participation in each competition separately.<br><br>Third parties and website links<br>We may transfer your information to other companies in our group or to our agents and contractors with us to assist us in related transactions in accordance with the terms of the privacy policy. For example, we may resort to a third party to help us deliver products to you, receive payments from you, and use them for statistics and marketing research purposes or to assist the customer service team. We may need to share information with a third party in order to protect against fraud and reduce credit risk. In the event that our company or part of it is sold, we may be forced to transfer our databases that include your personal information. Contrary to what is stipulated in the Privacy Policy, we will not sell or disclose your personal data to a third party without obtaining your prior consent unless it is necessary for the purposes stipulated in this Privacy Policy, or if we are required to do so by law. The site may contain third-party advertisements or links to other websites or frames of other sites. We inform you that we are not responsible for the privacy policy of any third party or the content of those policies applied in other sites, as well as that we are not responsible for any third party to whom we transfer 